 SZA 在欺凌和骚扰指控中为“美丽”的 Lizzo 提供支持https://www.nme.com/news/music/sza-supports-beautiful-lizzo-amid-harassment-allegations-big-grrrls-special-3509053?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=sza-supports-beautiful-lizzo-骚扰指控中的大女孩特别Kyann-Sian WilliamsWed, 04 Oct 2023 17:08:27 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopR&B https://www.nme.com/?p=3509053 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sza-lizzo-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="SZA 和利佐" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sza-lizzo-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sza-lizzo-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sza-lizzo-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sza-lizzo-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sza-lizzo-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sza-lizzo-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我真的祈祷每个人都能从中康复，因为每个人都应该得到治愈、感到安全、感受到被爱”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>首先出现了<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sza-supports-beautiful-lizzo-amid-harassment-allegations-big-grrrls-special-3509053">欺凌和骚扰指控，SZA 为“美丽”Lizzo 提供支持</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sza-lizzo-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="SZA 和利佐" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sza-lizzo-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sza-lizzo-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sza-lizzo-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sza-lizzo-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sza-lizzo-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-cont