时触摸裸体表演者。 </p><figure id="attachment_3466124" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3466124" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3466124" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Mad-Cool-2023-Andres-Iglesias.jpg" alt="Lizzo，Mad Cool 23。图片来源：Andres Iglesias" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Mad-Cool-2023-Andres-Iglesias.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Mad-Cool-2023-Andres-Iglesias-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Mad-Cool-2023-Andres-Iglesias-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Mad-Cool-2023-Andres-Iglesias-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Mad-Cool-2023-Andres-Iglesias-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Mad-Cool-2023-Andres-Iglesias-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3466124" class="wp-caption-text"> Lizzo，Mad Cool 23。图片来源：Andres Iglesias</figcaption></figure><p>利佐否认了这些指控，称其“令人愤慨”。上周，她要求主审法官<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-asks-judge-to-dismiss-ridiculous-harassment-lawsuit-3506381">驳回针对她的“虚假”案件</a>，并补充说看到她的性格受到这样的“批评”令人“失望”。</p><p>她的律师还表示，他们“打算在她胜诉后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-planning-to-sue-former-backup-dancers-for-malicious-prosecution-3487885">提起恶意起诉</a>，这些似是而非的指控被驳回”。他还补充道：“这起诉讼是一场骗局。”</p><p> “任何相反的说法都是荒谬的，我们期待在法庭上证明这一点，”利佐的团队在回应中写道。</p><p>两名起诉利佐性骚扰的舞者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzos-backing-dancers-claim-they-tried-to-settle-dispute-in-house-but-were-met-with-rebuttal-3479486">声称，他们“试图在内部”解决</a>此事，但遭到了“反驳”，而据报道， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-shouts-out-lizzo-during-atlanta-concert-amid-allegations-3483066">她的 14 名舞者因另一起纠纷获得了和解</a>。 Lizzo 的一些“Big Grrl”和“Big Boiiis”舞者也在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzos-big-grrl-dancers-praise-her-for-shattering-limitations-in-new-open-letter-3484966">一封公开信中赞扬了这位歌手</a>。</p><p>在其他新闻中，SZA 与 Drake 一起创作了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-enlists-sza-for-new-single-slime-you-3498888">《Slime You Out》</a> ，这是他即将发行的专辑《FOR ALL THE DOGS》中的一首单曲，该<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-faces-backlash-for-american-slaves-lyric-on-new-song-slime-you-out-3499459">歌曲因歌词提到奴隶制而引起争议</a>。上周，她还与 Jean Dawson 合作推出了简约、反思性的合作作品<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sza-jean-dawson-release-collaborative-new-single-new-single-no-szns-listen-video-watch-3503627">《No Szns》</a> 。</p><p>上个月，当莉佐的法律斗争仍在进行时，她在今年的黑人音乐联盟晚会上被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-accepts-quincy-jones-humanitarian-award-amidst-ongoing-legal-battles-3502672">授予昆西·琼斯人道主义奖</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>首先出现了<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sza-supports-beautiful-lizzo-amid-harassment-allegations-big-grrrls-special-3509053">欺凌和骚扰指控，SZA 为“美丽”Lizzo 提供支持</a>。</p> ;
