ges.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/krayzie-bone-Michael-Bezjian_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/krayzie-bone-Michael-Bezjian_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/krayzie-bone-Michael-Bezjian_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/krayzie-bone-Michael-Bezjian_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/krayzie-bone-Michael-Bezjian_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/krayzie-bone">Krayzie Bone</a>分享了他最近住院后的最新健康状况。</p><p>上个月，克雷齐·博恩（Krayzie Bone）——真名安东尼·亨德森（Anthony Henderson）—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/krayzie-bone-bone-thugs-n-harmony-hospitalised-bleeding-artery-lung-3505250">因肺部发现动脉出血而咳血，入院治疗</a>。亨德森立即接受了手术并戴上了呼吸机。</p><p>现在，这位<a href="/artists/bone-thugs-n-harmony" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bone Thugs-N-Harmony</a>说唱歌手贴出了一张他躺在医院病床上的照片，并举起了和平的手势。在 Instagram 的标题中，博恩仍然保持积极态度，称他在“为自己的生命而战”近一个半星期后“赢得了这场战斗”。</p><p> “简直就是为了生命而奋斗了九天，”他写道。 “这一次我才赢得了这场战斗，因为我知道耶和华上帝一直与我同在，为我而战。”</p><p>他继续说道：“永远不要认为生活是理所当然的，趁拥有它的时候享受它吧！感谢你们所有人的想法和祈祷，相信我，我需要他们中的每一个。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Cx9B_fTPMvI/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; he